                    <p class="service-card__description">Designing RESTful APIs and Microservices. Connecting systems seamlessly with solid documentation.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card__footer"><span>REST</span>•<span>GQL</span>•<span>Micro</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card service-card--purple">
                <div class="service-card__gradient"></div>
                <div class="service-card__content">
                    <div class="service-card__icon-wrapper service-card__icon-wrapper--purple">
                        <i data-lucide="rocket" class="service-card__icon service-card__icon--purple"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="service-card__title">Modernization</h3>
                    <p class="service-card__description">Transforming legacy systems into modern high-performance apps. Refactoring and stack migration.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card__footer"><span>Fix</span>•<span>Speed</span>•<span>Migrate</span></div>
